2011年8月，當局宣佈由[[瑞士|瑞士]][[施泰德鐵路|施泰德鐵路]]取得新電車的合約{{RefTag|name=newTramsGazette|1={{Cite Web|url=http://www.railwaygazette.com/nc/news/single-view/view/stadler-wins-london-tramlink-tram-order.html|title=Stadler wins London Tramlink tram order|publisher=[[Railway_Gazette_International|Railway Gazette International]]|date=2011-08-18|accessdate=2012-05-24|language=en|archive-date=2011-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110917051215/http://www.railwaygazette.com/nc/news/single-view/view/stadler-wins-london-tramlink-tram-order.html|dead-url=no}}}}。新電車為數六輛，屬於{{tsl|en|Variotram|Variobahn}}型號，五節編組。它們於2012年起投入服務{{RefTag|name=line4opens}}。

== 延伸計劃 ==
自通車以來，擴展輕軌電車路網一直是有關地區人士的討論焦點。以下列舉四項較受重視的延伸計劃{{RefTag|name=TramlinkUnofficialExtension|1={{Cite Web |url=http://www.tramlink.co.uk/extensions/index.shtml |title=Tramlink Extensions |work=Croydon Tramlink the Unofficial Site |author=S.J. Parascandolo |accessdate=2012-07-18 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120605044236/http://tramlink.co.uk/extensions/index.shtml |archivedate=2012-06-05 }}}}{{RefTag|name=atoCTX|1={{Cite Web |url=http://www.alwaystouchout.com/project/19 |title=Tramlink to Sutton and Mitcham |work=alwaystouchout.com |date=2007-01-27 |accessdate=2012-07-18 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071111080806/http://www.alwaystouchout.com/project/19 |archivedate=2007-11-11 }}}}{{RefTag|name=davrosF|1={{Cite Web|url=http://www.davros.org/rail/culg/future.html|title=Future Proposals|work=Clive's UndergrounD Line Guides|author=Clive Feather|date=2011-12-03|accessdate=2012-07-18|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201025024410/http://www.davros.org/rail/culg/future.html|dead-url=no}}}} ：

* 由溫布頓站向南經摩頓站（轉乘[[倫敦地鐵北線|倫敦地鐵北線]]）到達薩頓
* 自米傑姆站向南、北分別延伸至薩頓及國鐵{{link-en|圖亭站|Tooting railway station}}。其中北延段途經[[倫敦地鐵北線|倫敦地鐵北線]]的[[圖亭大道站|圖亭大道站]]
* 由克羅伊登市中心的環線分別向南、北延伸。南延線往[[普爾雷|普爾雷]]，北延線往[[斯切咸|斯切咸]]
* 從夏靈頓路站向''西''延伸，沿國鐵水晶宮線前往國鐵[[水晶宮站|水晶宮站]]

倫敦當局曾就往水晶宮的延伸線進行研究，但至今仍因資金問題而未有任何實質進展{{RefTag|name=CTBoris|1={{Cite news|url=http://www.thisiscroydontoday.co.uk/Boris-Johnson-promises-tramlink-extension-Crystal/story-16183356-detail/story.html|title=Boris Johnson promises tramlink extension to Crystal Palace and Sutton|date=2012-05-30|accessdate=2012-07-18|publisher=Croydon Today|language=en}}{{Dead link|date=2019年3月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}{{dead link|date=2018年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}}}。

